ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectFederal Contribution to assist Hog Producers - Swine Flu (H1N1) in Alberta.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide for federal contributions to assist a hog producer whose herd was affected by swine flu (H1N1) in Alberta.
